http://ionicframework.com/docs/guide/installation.html

export ANDROID_HOME=$HOME/Android/Sdk
export PATH=$PATH:$ANDROID_HOME/tools

If want it to make it permanent just add those lines in the ~/.bashrc file


ionic install # install all ionic ibraries mentioned in the package.json

ionic build android # create apk in /platforms/android/build/outputs/apk folder

ionic run android # run in mobile

ionic serve [-l] # iOS and Android together

ionic serve android




